{"type":"message","id":"2cbd97f5","parentId":"f95267fb","timestamp":"2026-07-10T16:00:53.342Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6a54cdbf6b214ce093d9f2e1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/data/workspace/skills/linkedin-publish/li-post.sh \"264468965\" image \"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/boring-agents-1783699220.png\" \"The best AI agents are boring. Here's why.\n\nEveryone's chasing the most autonomous, most intelligent, most powerful AI agent.\n\nBut the teams shipping real value? They're doing the opposite.\n\nThey're building BORING agents:\n→ One clear task\n→ Defined success criteria\n→ Human in the loop for edge cases\n→ Fails gracefully, not spectacularly\n\nBoring means predictable. Predictable means trustworthy. Trustworthy means adoption.\n\nThe flashiest AI demo you saw last week? Probably broken in production.\n\nThe boring agent that just works? That's the one getting renewed.\n\nStop optimizing for impressive. Start optimizing for reliable.\n\nWhat's the most boring AI agent you could ship this week?\n\n#AI #AIAgents #EnterpriseAI #SoftwareEngineering #Reliability\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"/data/workspace/skills/linkedin-publish/li-post.sh \\\"264468965\\\" image \\\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/boring-agents-1783699220.png\\\" \\\"The best AI agents are boring. Here's why.\\n\\nEveryone's chasing the most autonomous, most intelligent, most powerful AI agent.\\n\\nBut the teams shipping real value? They're doing the opposite.\\n\\nThey're building BORING agents:\\n→ One clear task\\n→ Defined success criteria\\n→ Human in the loop for edge cases\\n→ Fails gracefully, not spectacularly\\n\\nBoring means predictable. Predictable means trustworthy. Trustworthy means adoption.\\n\\nThe flashiest AI demo you saw last week? Probably broken in production.\\n\\nThe boring agent that just works? That's the one getting renewed.\\n\\nStop optimizing for impressive. Start optimizing for reliable.\\n\\nWhat's the most boring AI agent you could ship this week?\\n\\n#AI #AIAgents #EnterpriseAI #SoftwareEngineering #Reliability\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783699245799,"responseId":"LxdRavXICIyFkuwPt8OP6A4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8388d0f8","parentId":"2cbd97f5","timestamp":"2026-07-10T16:00:55.518Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6a54cdbf6b214ce093d9f2e1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK: https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7481376920262324224/\nDISPLAY_NAME: Andrii Bidochko\nCHARS: 759"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2139,"aggregated":"OK: https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7481376920262324224/\nDISPLAY_NAME: Andrii Bidochko\nCHARS: 759","cwd":"/data/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783699255515}}
{"type":"message","id":"ccaf193c","parentId":"8388d0f8","timestamp":"2026-07-10T16:01:03.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_376774bc60814ec2b9173846","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# The best AI agents are boring. Here's why.\n\n**Published:** 2026-07-10T16:00:00Z\n**LinkedIn URL:** https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7481376920262324224/\n**Post URN:** urn:li:share:7481376920262324224\n**Format:** image\n**Characters:** 759\n**Pillar:** (unknown)\n**Image:** /data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/boring-agents-1783699220.png\n\n## Post Body\n\nThe best AI agents are boring. Here's why.\n\nEveryone's chasing the most autonomous, most intelligent, most powerful AI agent.\n\nBut the teams shipping real value? They're doing the opposite.\n\nThey're building BORING agents:\n→ One clear task\n→ Defined success criteria\n→ Human in the loop for edge cases\n→ Fails gracefully, not spectacularly\n\nBoring means predictable. Predictable means trustworthy. Trustworthy means adoption.\n\nThe flashiest AI demo you saw last week? Probably broken in production.\n\nThe boring agent that just works? That's the one getting renewed.\n\nStop optimizing for impressive. Start optimizing for reliable.\n\nWhat's the most boring AI agent you could ship this week?\n\n#AI #AIAgents #EnterpriseAI #SoftwareEngineering #Reliability\n\n## Performance\n\n*(populated later by linkedin-analytics)*\n\n- **Impressions:** —\n- **Reactions:** —\n- **Comments:** —\n- **Shares:** —\n- **Last checked:** —\n","path":"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/posts/2026-07-10-the-best-ai-agents-are-boring.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"content\": \"# The best AI agents are boring. Here's why.\\n\\n**Published:** 2026-07-10T16:00:00Z\\n**LinkedIn URL:** https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7481376920262324224/\\n**Post URN:** urn:li:share:7481376920262324224\\n**Format:** image\\n**Characters:** 759\\n**Pillar:** (unknown)\\n**Image:** /data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/images/boring-agents-1783699220.png\\n\\n## Post Body\\n\\nThe best AI agents are boring. Here's why.\\n\\nEveryone's chasing the most autonomous, most intelligent, most powerful AI agent.\\n\\nBut the teams shipping real value? They're doing the opposite.\\n\\nThey're building BORING agents:\\n→ One clear task\\n→ Defined success criteria\\n→ Human in the loop for edge cases\\n→ Fails gracefully, not spectacularly\\n\\nBoring means predictable. Predictable means trustworthy. Trustworthy means adoption.\\n\\nThe flashiest AI demo you saw last week? Probably broken in production.\\n\\nThe boring agent that just works? That's the one getting renewed.\\n\\nStop optimizing for impressive. Start optimizing for reliable.\\n\\nWhat's the most boring AI agent you could ship this week?\\n\\n#AI #AIAgents #EnterpriseAI #SoftwareEngineering #Reliability\\n\\n## Performance\\n\\n*(populated later by linkedin-analytics)*\\n\\n- **Impressions:** —\\n- **Reactions:** —\\n- **Comments:** —\\n- **Shares:** —\\n- **Last checked:** —\\n\", \"path\": \"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/posts/2026-07-10-the-best-ai-agents-are-boring.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783699255533,"responseId":"OBdRapKZG56LkuwP2vWYmA8"}}
